}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{The course enables a better understanding of the principles of the 
labour market\'2e It analyses also its wider social connotations and 
links to other disciplines\'2e}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{\~}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{{\b
Learning outcomes and competences: }}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{Upon successful completion of this course, students will be able to 
\line
\_ apply economic theory to the labour market\line
\_ build a model of behaviour and decision\_making of various players 
on the labour market and the impact of its various institutions\line
\_ explain a role of the state on the labour market\line
\_ apply models of labour market to real world situations\line
\_ assess and evaluate various methods of solving labour market problems 
with respect to their economic efficiency\line
\line
}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{\~}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
